  KhoaN3--khi2-lai5 si7 pe7-a2-kiaN2 hiaN-ti7, <BR>  Kang7-khoan2 san3 kah kui2 beh thoa--khi3, <BR>  Koah na5-au5 e5 oan-siu5, <BR>  Ou2 bak8-chiu-jin5 e5 chheh-hun7, <BR>  Ui3 tiang5-si5 khai-si2 ? 
  Soa-bou5 ta-soaN si7 Ah-hu-gan2 (Afganistan) e5 seng3-te7, <BR>  Tak8-jit8 kui7--loh8-khi3 pai3-sin5 ngou7 pian3, <BR>  Ki-to2 hoe2-sio-chhu3 e5 chheh-hun7 <BR>  Kiong5-kan cha-bou2 e5 oan-siu5, <BR>  Lu2 pai3 lu2 che7. 
  Sin5 ti7 in tiong-kan oe7 chit8-tiau5 thih-soaN3, <BR>  Lang5 be7-tang3 lai5-ong2 kiaN5--koe3, <BR>  Kan-na chheng3-chi2 toaN7 be7-soah, <BR>  Kap toa7-phau3 pong7 hou7 in long2-chong2 si2. 
  Si2--khi3-e5 khoaN3--khi2-lai5 ma7 chin-seng5 <BR>  In pe7-a2-kiaN2 hiaN-ti7, <BR>  Seng pak hit-siang e5, <BR>  Kiau7 hit-ki kim chhui3-khi2, <BR>  Chheng-sng3 oan-siu5 e5 khiam3-che3. 
  Phoa3-pou3 pau e5 sin-si <BR>  Hou7 Ah-hu-gan2 e5 soa-hong chhoe ta--khi3, <BR>  Chiok-che7 teng7-khok-khok un ti7 hia, <BR>  Chhin-chhiuN7 cho3-hoe2 teh pai3 Ah-lah e5 sin5 : <BR>  Sin5 be7 be7 ki3--tit, <BR>  Lang5 long2 bo5 iau3-kin2. 
  （Tai5-bun5-tong-sin3 Te7 101 ki5, 2002 ni5 7 goeh8) 
</CL>
